description:
** No Broker's Fee! ** Perched atop historic and tree-lined Thomas Park, this bi-level 2BR / 1.5 bath unit occupies the second and third floors of a charming 6 unit building. Enter to find the primary bedroom, guest bedroom, and full bathroom on the lower level. New carpeting in second bedroom and new paint throughout. The primary hosts a spacious attached deck space and walk-in closet. The upper level hosts a truly unique main living area with vaulted high ceilings, a gas fireplace, and sliding doors leading out to your second private deck with sweeping city views. A fully applianced kitchen and half bathroom with in-unit laundry can also be found on the top floor. Gas heating, electricity, and cable/internet are paid for by tenants. Basement storage may be available as well. Small pets may be permitted on a case by case basis.

Owner pays for water. Tenants are responsible for gas heating, electricity, cable/internet
